  "title": "feat(Configure): add configure parameters in search state",
  "body": "This PR add to the search state all configure parameters. That way, if you perform some changes to them when listening to `onSearchStateChange` it will be taken into account. \r\n\r\nI used the `transitionState` function of the connector to be able to add those parameters to the state without the need of calling refine (that triggers a new search). It might not be the most obvious name though. ",
